              <h3 id="docx-and-pdf-two-of-your-favorite-file-types" class="heading-s">DOCX and PDF, two of your favorite file types</h3>
              <p class="body-m">It's easy to create new content or gather your thoughts in a word processor, while PDF is the trusted format to share a file. PDF preserves your formatting and can reliably be opened on any supported device. When you want to easily switch between DOCX files and PDF format for free, look no further than the Acrobat online converter.</p>
